Ok limbo main here there too many ways to play limbo but here are some of the best
1) max duration medium range high efficiency 
In this build you use your cataclysm for defense and safe zone for you and week team mates
Banish is for rescue Cetus drones or if someone requested it can also be used with statis against small groups of enemies 
His third ability is a trap u activate it on rifted enemies so that once they get out of the rift it sends them back also if u dash and rift urself u can shoot into cataclysm from far away

2)short duration same range and efficiency 
This one is more difficult to use but basically u use your first and third to make groups of enemies go into an infinite loop of knock downs were u can kill them one by one cataclysm can be used to get bigger amounts of enemies into the rift
